Hello Welltuck and welcome to the community boards.

The best way to see if there are living decendents on this site is to put Myrtle's name into the Search Trees box above. You will see that there are two other members with her in their tree. You can contact them for further information. Cx.

Hi there! I understand that this is a 9 year old thread so my reply may not be seen but I am pretty sure I am one of the descendants of the Myrtle A Stone you are referring to (buried in Wentworth Falls). I have only just recently started to look into my family tree. She was my maternal grandmother's mother. I was born long after she passed away so I really know nothing about her unfortunately.

Tiffany
